\v 10 Won na won santide fenfe al…î d…înxui naxan …≤…õr…õma a yire masuxu ma.
\q1 Won birama yanyi ra, al…î won na …≤…õr…õfe dimi nan kui.
\q1 Won luxi n…õ al…î mixi faxaxi s…õnb…õmae tagi.
