\v 11 Won xurundunma al…î burun subee,
\q1 won wa xui raminima al…î ganb…õ.
\q1 Won gbe …≤…îx…î…õ nan fenfe, k…în…î won mu a s…ît…îma.
\q1 Won xaxili tixi kisi nan na, k…în…î a makuya won na.
